  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 150\u000430C (300\u00020F).",
    "Rinse the pancetta and cut it into 1-inch cubes. Then roast it in the oven for 10 minutes, or until crispy.",
    "Chop the onions and saut\b4 them in a pan until they're soft.",
    "Add the carrots and potatoes to the pan and saut\b4 them for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the Bhuna curry paste and vegetable broth to the pan, and stir well.",
    "Add the roasted pancetta to the pan, and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Transfer the mixture to the claypot, cover it, and cook in the oven for 30 minutes, or until the stew is heated through.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
  ],
